</paragraph>
<paragraph id="666036ACFF9DFF9CBDAABC5B11E48E72" blockId="106.[151,1437,249,716]" box="[151,1436,313,334]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">
<keyLead id="DD2E9599FF9DFF9CBDAABC5B11E48E72" box="[151,1436,313,334]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">– Mandible with 3 inner teeth.............................................................................. 3</keyLead>
